						<summary>

						<p>On a pillar in the verandah of the Bhīmēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>Sarvalōkāśraya Vishṇuvardhana-mahārāja, A.D. 1133.</p>						

						<p>This is dated in the 10th regnal year, and Śaka 1055, solar eclipse. (A.D. 1133).</p>						

						<p>Records the installation of Bhīmēśvara at Uṇḍavelli by Kaṇḍravāḍi Bhīmarāja and registers a gift of two <hi rend="italic">Khaṇḍugas</hi> of land by him for worship and offerings in the temple. Also records the construction of a shrine for Gaṇapati in the Śiva temple by Paṇḍi-raḍḍi, son of Kūchenaraḍḍi of Uṇḍavelli.</p>						

						</summary>
